# Design System Rules

Read `.ai/context/design-system.md` and `.ai/patterns/ui-composition.md` before broad UI work.

## Key reminders

- Preserve the mature neutral shadcn-style baseline unless a palette change is explicitly requested.
- Use shared theme tokens instead of hardcoded colors.
- Use CVA, `cn()`, named exports, and `data-slot` for shared UI components.
- Avoid nested cards and decorative-only layouts in app workflows.
